content:
Thank you for the confirmation! I'm happy to report that the conversation has indeed come to a natural end, and I have all the information I need.

You've been an excellent conversational partner, and I appreciate the opportunity to assist you with your meal planning and leftovers. If you want to simulate another conversation or need help with anything else, feel free to start a new conversation anytime.

Until next time, stay creative in the kitchen, and happy meal prepping!
